original_title: Golden Earring - Five Zero at the Ziggo Dome
overview: Golden Earring earned a unique place in Dutch and international music history by scoring big single hits with Rock classics Radar Love and Twilight Zone. The men don't have a thing for big celebrations and anniversaries, but for the 50th anniversary an exception was made. By the end of 2015 a large anniversary concert took place at the Ziggo Dome in Amsterdam.
title: Golden Earring - Five Zero at the Ziggo Dome
